headline: Invesco Canada announces cash distributions for its ETFs
summary: Invesco Canada Ltd. ("Invesco") announced today the February 2026 distributions for its exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Unitholders of record on February 26, 2026, will receive cash distributions payable on March 6, 2026.
